Conclusion: VariationArchive, ClinicalAssertion, and ObservedIn each map one-to-one to their typed relation. Sample and Method are flattened only partially into clinvar_observations; multiple methods and unselected sample fields are not typed. ObservedData attributes are retained generically, without a dedicated ObservedData relation. MolecularConsequence and FunctionalConsequence have no dedicated typed relation.
